{
  "stem": "21582.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we had a-- a quota we had to do, complete, a-- a designated amount of that work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- there was-- there were Germans who were watching us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was a German woman who would, you know, if you fell asleep, a slap, slap.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we had to somehow keep a little bit clean.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was the risk-taker in the family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My sister, was less of-- she was always the one who would say, oh, it's so undignifying, our existence.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Let's surrender.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Let's give up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my mother and I were the ones that said-- you know, no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the factory had-- the work that we did was only one small assignment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There were other-- other kinds of work, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there were big-- big-- big machines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was a very noisy place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And one of the machines cleaned the bullets, the shells.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so there was a sudsy water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if you had-- a-- at great risk, because it was sabotage-- you would walk with a can that was supposed to be your soup can with-- that had a little wire attached.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you'd walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you would walk by and dip and get that sudsy water that you-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that-- we took that sudsy water, so we can wash ourselves.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What we would do every now and then-- now I had scabies already on my head, on my scalp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was going to wash my hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my sister met me in the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were going to really quickly wash my hair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My sister and her friends, in her fear, forgot to add cold water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the water was scalding.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
